           FUNCTION ALL INTRINSIC.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  W-USERNAME               PIC X(30) VALUE SPACES.
       01  W-ENTER                  PIC X.
       01  W-COMP                   PIC 99.
       01  W-PRINTCOMMAND.
